Answer for Exercise 2 -

Program –
names = ['Angela', 'Rujeth', 'Shyra']

msg = "Hello, Good Morning " + names[0].title() + "!" print(msg)

msg = "Hello, Good Morning " + names[1].title() + "!" print(msg)

msg = "Hello, Good Morning " + names[2].title() + "!" print(msg)

Output –
Hello, Good Morning Angela! 
Hello, Good Morning Rujeth! 
Hello, Good Morning Shyra!

